Requirements
 1. GO 1.10 installed
 2. Postgres installed

Install
 1. Setup database by running:
     psql -h <DB_IP_ADDRESS> -p 5432 -U postgres -f sql/PersistentStorage.sql
     **** Warning! - this script deletes and replaces "0chain" database and miner user ****
 2. Change the variable psql_host in Server/go/0chain/0chain_db.go to the correct postgres server IP address. 
 3. Run ./Install.sh

Run
 1. ./bin/PersistentStorageServer 

Sanity Test (while server is running)
 1. ./QuickTest/ServerTest.sh <YOUR_IP_ADDRESS> 8082
